				<div class="flex items-center justify-between ">
				  <p class="Q">薬と併用しても大丈夫ですか？</p>
                  <svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" :class="selected == 5 ? 'rotate-180' : 'rotate-0'" class="inline w-4 h-4 mt-1 ml-1 transition-transform duration-200 transform md:-mt-1"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
